about.summary: An in-memory LRU cache for python

name: py_lru_cache
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "py_lru_cache" %}
{% set version = "0.1.4" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 02df33684e13e1a78987bf9f8b0ac90210952857d9d12d1cf83fd0c906456af0

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - lru

about:
  home: https://github.com/stucchio/Python-LRU-cache
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'An in-memory LRU cache for python'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ericmjl
